         <td class="contentNormal"> <p>Welcome to Pusthaka 1.0.</p> <p>With Pusthaka, you can access the services offered by the UCSC Library.</p> <p> The UCSC Library provides its service to the staff and students of the <a href="http://www.ucsc.cmb.ac.lk/">University of Colombo School of Computing</a> and hosts around 8000 books.</p> <p>If you are a member of the library, you may <a href="_login.php">login</a> to Pusthaka and access features such as online search and online researvation of books. If you are a member but still haven't registered with Pusthaka, please <a href="register.php">register now</a>.<br> Please make sure that you are familiar with the UCSC Library <a href="_rules.php">Rules and Regulations</a> </p> <p>Even if you are just visitng you may still use our <a href="book_search.php">online search</a>. </p> </td> 
